(ivcwrw) nIc (ijhw) pqMgw (Awpxy) ipAwry (jgdy-dIvy) dy ipAwr ivc (ieqnw) msq ho jWdw hY (ik ipAwry nUM) Xwd kridAW ausnUM Awpxy srIr dI suD-buD nhIN rihMdI[
